700
00:54:58,860 --> 00:55:01,600
I'll happily let him treat me. Huwag kang mag-alala.

701
00:55:01,600 --> 00:55:05,660
Mahusay. buti naman. Mabuti.

702
00:55:05,660 --> 00:55:07,080
Bumalik ka sa loob.

703
00:55:07,080 --> 00:55:09,390
Sige. Salamat!

704
00:55:12,320 --> 00:55:13,760
Tagumpay.

705
00:55:25,920 --> 00:55:28,630
[MS. Seo Jong Hui]

706
00:55:51,930 --> 00:55:53,750
Mr. Jo Hyeon Woo?

707
00:55:53,750 --> 00:55:57,320
